  "onboardingWelcomeMoreTitle": "About the trial and license",
  "onboardingWelcomeCopyLong": "At the end of the trial, you and your partners can choose to continue by purchasing a $4 license per person. Each participant in the plan must have a license.\n\nThis license funds development and maintenance. There will NEVER be ads in the app.\n\nYour data is not used in any way: it stays on your device (and the participants’ devices) and nowhere else. The data belongs to you.\n\nIf you don’t renew the license, you won’t be able to add new data, but you will be able to export existing data.",
